intro_lines = ["Right — here's our last Tutor-Yale stop. Elmwood Avenue, six letters, houses 1401 to 1406.", "Now, some of this mail's got bits missing. Names, numbers, a town smudged funny — you know the drill.", "Use what you do know first. A sender, a poster on a door, a house you've already ruled out — anything helps.", "Finish these six and we'll call Tutor-Yale done. Off you go."]
